257696.name: Turbocharged Crimson Twin Swords
257696.tooltip: They're a pair of hardcore killers, a warrior's best friends, nitro-burning and blazing twin trails down a highway to hell.

257708.name: Turbocharged Crimson Lance
257708.tooltip: Behold the lancer's spear and shield, born and built to stand between the pure and the profane...the helpless and the horrific.

257720.name: Turbocharged Crimson Greatsword
257720.tooltip: Precision-tooled mayhem in the hands of a slayer, red as fire and blood and all things terrible and wonderful.

257732.name: Turbocharged Crimson Axe
257732.tooltip: Whosoever blocks the berserker's path will know the axe and taste its bloody wrath.

257744.name: Turbocharged Crimson Disk

257756.name: Turbocharged Crimson Bow

257768.name: Turbocharged Crimson Staff
257768.tooltip: It's a driveshaft of death, red-lined and ready to roar for the high priests of horsepower!

257780.name: Turbocharged Crimson Scepter
257780.tooltip: Welcome, mystics madame and monsieur, to mechanical mayhem, lathed in heaven for your hand and your hand only!

257792.name: Turbocharged Crimson Powerfists
257792.tooltip: Built for brawlers, with a one-two punch that pounds the blacktop and punishes the pavement!

257804.name: Turbocharged Crimson Arcannon
257804.tooltip: For gunners with guts, all revved up and cruising for a shot at glory!

257816.name: Turbocharged Crimson Glaive
257816.tooltip: Hit the nitro and open up the throttle! It's time for the flight of the valkyrie, and she's in no mood for idle pursuits!

257828.name: Turbocharged Crimson Scythes
257828.tooltip: Grab death with both hands and let the reaper hit the road!

257840.name: Turbocharged Crimson Shuriken
257840.tooltip: It's a shooting star for the ninja who drinks nitro and spits out spite!

257852.name: Turbocharged Chrome Twin Swords
257852.tooltip: The way of the warrior is mapped out in slaughter and chromium steel, screaming for blood.

257864.name: Turbocharged Chrome Lance
257864.tooltip: Lets a lancer roar through the valley of death and despair with doom in one hand and defiance in the other.

257876.name: Turbocharged Chrome Greatsword
257876.tooltip: Behold the slayer of beasts, and the living weapon that wields it!

257888.name: Turbocharged Chrome Axe
257888.tooltip: It's fury in form and function, a berserker's best buddy in the wastes and the wilds!

257900.name: Turbocharged Chrome Disk
257900.tooltip: Nothing stands before the sorcerer whose will is made of solid steel!

257912.name: Turbocharged Chrome Bow
257912.tooltip: Gives an archer the attitude of an archangel, with arrows that whisper words of apocalypse.

257924.name: Turbocharged Chrome Staff
257924.tooltip: A solid steel symphony sent from on high to answer the prayers of the priests of the open road!

257936.name: Turbocharged Chrome Scepter
257936.tooltip: The universe is a five-speed dream machine, and this baby lets a mystic shift it into high gear!

257948.name: Turbocharged Chrome Powerfists

257960.name: Turbocharged Chrome Arcannon

257972.name: Turbocharged Chrome Glaive
257972.tooltip: You're the angel of death...a high-velocity valkyrie on the express lane to glory!

257984.name: Turbocharged Chrome Scythes

258200.name: Supercharged Silver Axe

258224.name: Supercharged Silver Bow

258248.name: Supercharged Silver Scepter

258260.name: Supercharged Silver Powerfists

258272.name: Supercharged Silver Arcannon
258272.tooltip: It breathes in magic and spits out fury!

258284.name: Supercharged Silver Glaive

258296.name: Supercharged Silver Scythes

258308.name: Supercharged Silver Shuriken
